'''
Write a python code that sum up(index) the position of elements in a given list if the element is negative.
    note: Do not we any built-in fuctions.

You are given a list that involves lists. The innor lists involves 10Ã¼zeri9 numbers writa a code that count # of list that involves at least 1 negative number.

Q1: e.g. : [2,5.-1,4,-3,8]
